Title: Everybody Dies
Plot: Facing a 6-month jail term, and the realization that he won't be there for Wilson at the end, House finds himself examining his entire life while contemplating a dismal future without his best friend.
Writer: David Shore, Peter Blake, Eli Attie
GuestStars: Andre Braugher, Anne Dudek, Jennifer Morrison, Kal Penn, Amber Tamblyn, Sela Ward
